Estrutura

Rung
  Elements (Contat,Coil, Block) Brach in Branch out
                                |-> Elemts 

Element save its position and BBox (so to get end will ne pos.x+size.x)
When Add a new Element Calc Its Position, relative to line/brach and Update Line/Brunch BBox
When Add new Branch Calc its Position, base on Line Heigh and Element positon

  

                                
                                    
    